column1: Web Site|Meet Loretta|On the Issues|Helping You|Newsroom|Contact MeDear Friend -While the number of Californians who have enrolled in quality, affordable healthcare is impressive and far exceeds the rest of the nation, there is much to be done in the next 17 days.
